  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM6.6">
<l>maṟporu tōḷuṭai vācutēvā valviṉai yēṉṟuyil koṇṭavāṟē</l>
<l>yiṟṟai yiraviṭai yēmatteṉṉai yiṉṉaṇai mēliṭṭa kaṉṟunīpōy</l>
<l>aṟṟai yiravumōr piṟṟaināḷu marivaiya rōṭu maṇaintuvantāy</l>
<l>eṟṟukku nīyeṉ maruṅkilvantā yemperu māṉī yeḻuntaruḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Vāsudeva with shoulders that fought the wrestlers!</l>
<l>As [soon as] I, with forceful karma, fell asleep tonight, during the middle watch,</l>
<l>You placed me in the plesant bed and went away.</l>
<l>That night and the following day, You came embracing women.</l>
<l>For what have You come by my side [now]? Our Lord! Be gracious [enough] to leave!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
